---3. `.gitignore`This file ensures that system files and temporary data do not clutter your GitHub history.```text# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files__pycache__/*.py[cod]*$py.class# Jupyter Notebook Checkpoints.ipynb_checkpoints*/.ipynb_checkpoints/*# Environments & Virtual Environments.env.venvenv/venv/# Data Files (Keep repo clean)*.csv*.xlsx*.zip*.gz*.png# Operating System Files.DS_StoreThumbs.db